 1. **Walk me through a decoder layer.** Input тЖТ RMSNorm тЖТ QKV projection (fused) тЖТ per-head norm тЖТ RoPE тЖТ flash attention (reads/writes KV cache) тЖТ output projection. Then RMSNorm тЖТ gate+up projection (fused) тЖТ SiLU gating тЖТ down projection. Residual connections wrap both sub-blocks.
